title: Chinese capsule damaged by space-junk strike returns to Earth (video)
description: The first emergency operation in the history of China's human spaceflight program ended on Jan. 19 when an uncrewed Shenzhou 20 capsule damaged by a space-junk strike came safely down to Earth.
